model

Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Element

  • public class Element
extends java.lang.Object
    Class contain all data about one segment of maze. Each maze is list of "Elements". Its a part of engineering project prepared by author at Silesian University of Technology, Gliwice
    Version:
    2.0 2016-01-22
    Author:
    Mariusz Nowak

      • isAscending

        public boolean isAscending()
        You can use this method if you want to check that segment is ascending. It means that: - if segment is horizontal then end of segment is on the right side. - if segment is vertical then end of segment is higher then start.
        Returns:
        indicator of direction. True if segment is ascending
